        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2937311" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9536334301611105713">This book was a waste of my time. Think of an old guy yelling at a bunch of kids to get off his lawn. Then put that sentence in really good grammar, and that is this book.<br/><br/>It&apos;s overwhelmingly pretentious. As far as I am concerned, it generally ignores the way language moves to apparent regression when in fact it is merely changing, as it always does.</span>
  <span id="freeText9536334301611105713" style="display:none">This book was a waste of my time. Think of an old guy yelling at a bunch of kids to get off his lawn. Then put that sentence in really good grammar, and that is this book.<br /><br />It's overwhelmingly pretentious. As far as I am concerned, it generally ignores the way language moves to apparent regression when in fact it is merely changing, as it always does.</span>
